{
  "stem": "12029.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She was there in the country, and we were pleased.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went out one day with-- you see, I didn't have a coat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a coat, but it had to be altered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then [INAUDIBLE] daughter went with me to a dressmaker to alter me the coat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I came back, I was stopped by two women.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They hit me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything what I wear-- had on me they took away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They blackmailed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a gold bracelet, a watch, a chain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know that I would be black-- and all the money what I had they took away, and they hit me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew that she'd done it, but I couldn't help myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The same time, the children came back from-- from the holiday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the little girl-- her name was at the time [INAUDIBLE]-- didn't come back with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we were very worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Arnold went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said he must have her back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she said, no, she's OK and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, no, she must come back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when they brought her back, she looked like a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But we couldn't take her to us, because we had to leave the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I was blackmailed again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we had to leave and to go to that flat, to that old woman's flat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the flat where mommy was there with Markusfeld.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we were in that flat, we were under padlock and key.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't cook.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when you went to the toilet, you were scared to pull the chain.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
